    <tags>game eternal-city skotos praetor mud gui tui</tags>
    <summary>Desktop and terminal client for The Eternal City</summary>
    <description>
Praetor is a client for The Eternal City (TEC). This package installs both the
desktop GUI (`praetor`, added to the Start Menu) and the terminal client
(`praetor-tui`), with authentication, Lua scripting automation, and a minimap
renderer.
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/cyber-godzilla/praetor/releases/tag/v@VERSION@

Upgrade note: the `praetor` command is now the desktop GUI. The terminal client
is available as `praetor-tui`.</releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
</package>
